OL,3,CUnited Utilities water bills could
OL,4,Crise by #33 million next year
OL,6,FUnited Utilities customers could see a
OL,7,Frise in their water bills after a
OL,8,Freport by water regulator Ofwat.
OL,10,FThe company's performance in a number
OL,11,Fof key areas mean it will be permitted
OL,12,Fto increase bills by #33.2 million
OL,13,Fnext year.
OL,15,FOfwat has said the figures are
OL,16,Fprovisional until it completes a
OL,17,Freview process in December, when the
OL,18,Fexact amount will be finalised .
