OL,3,CUnited Utilities water bills could
OL,4,Crise by #33 million next year
OL,6,FThis comes after the regulator
OL,7,Fconfirmed water bills in England and
OL,8,FWales are set to rise by #19 a year on
OL,9,Faverage over the next five years.
OL,11,FOfwat found that Cumbria's water
OL,12,Fsupplier had one of the highest
OL,13,Fincreases in the number of pollution
OL,14,Fincidents between 2022 and 2023, with
OL,15,Fa rise of 71% in 2023 when compared
OL,16,Fwith the previous 12 months.
OL,18,FThe report also found that the company
OL,19,Fperformed worse than the level they
OL,20,Fcommitted to on drinking water quality.
