OL,3,CUnited Utilities water bills could
OL,4,Crise by #33 million next year
OL,6,FHowever, United Utilities was ranked
OL,7,Faverage overall, performing better in
OL,8,Fareas such as looking after customers
OL,9,Fwho need additional support and in
OL,10,Fmeeting its target for reducing leaks.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for United Utilities
OL,13,Fsaid: "We have tough targets set by
OL,14,FOfwat and we're pleased that we have
OL,15,Fmet 80% of our performance commitments.
