OL,4,Crise by #33 million next year
OL,6,FBut the company acknowledged that
OL,7,Fthere is more work to do to improve
OL,8,Fperformance.
OL,10,FThey added: "Annual rainfall in 2023
OL,11,Fwas exceptionally high across the
OL,12,FNorth West ` with it being second
OL,13,Fwettest since 1871.
OL,15,F"This had an adverse impact on service
OL,16,Ffor customers, with increased
OL,17,Finstances of flooding and spills from
OL,18,Four storm overflows.
